                           used).</seg>
                        <date>Late 19th - first half of the 20th century (?)</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>ይዲ፡ for ይበል፡ ዲያቆን፡</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; incipit of Texts I-II; directives to
                           the ministers and their abbreviations; titles of the books to be read;
                           initial passages of the reading; elements of the punctuation signs;
                           elements of Ethiopic numerals.
 On the incipit page of Text I (fol.
                           3r), a few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines).</seg>
                     </handNote>
